the second season of house premiered on september 13, 2005 and ended on may 23, 2006. during the season, house tries to cope with his feelings for his ex-girlfriend stacy warner, who, after house diagnosed her husband with acute intermittent porphyria, has taken a job in the legal department of princeton-plainsboro hospital. sela ward's chemistry with laurie in the final two episodes of season one was strong enough to have her character return in seven episodes of the second season.